            <div class="content-box" style="padding-bottom: 10%;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Join Us Today</h2>
                <p>Ready to simplify your meal experience? <strong>PSU Eats</strong> is here to make your life easier.
                    Join our community today and start enjoying the convenience of pre-ordering your meals!</p>
                <a href="/home" class="cta-button">Start Ordering Now</a>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 PSU Eats. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

</body>

</html>